        {
          "dialogueLines": [
            {
              "speaker": "Storyteller",
              "text": "Well past the flaming river escalates the hidden stair toward the most well-guarded, splendorous environment within the Underworld: the heavenly Elysium, home eternal to the greatest souls which ever lived."
